dct_title_s: Republic of Uzbekistan / the map compiled and prepared for print by the State Scientific Industrial Enterprise "Cartographiya" in 2008 ; editors E.V. Manikova ; technical editor   T.S. Gurova ; designer by I.G. Batalova (Uzbekistan)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Map shows boundaries according to political-administrative significance: Republic Karakalpakstan, international, oblasts, and districts; railways, 4 classes of roads, caravan tracks. Includes distance tables, and color illustrations. © Statcomlandgeodescadastre.
dct_publisher_sm: Tashkent : State Committee of the Republic of Uzbekistan for Land Resources, Geodesy, Cartography, and State Cadastre, 2008.
